DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME IN ( SELECT DATE_DAY.DAY_NAME FROM DATE_DAY WHERE DATE_DAY.YEAR = 1993 AND DATE_DAY.MONTH_NUMBER = 3 AND DATE_DAY.DAY_NUMBER = 9 ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
( SELECT DISTINCT AIRLINE.AIRLINE_NAME , AIRLINE.AIRLINE_CODE FROM AIRLINE WHERE ( AIRLINE.AIRLINE_CODE = ' CP ' OR AIRLINE.AIRLINE_CODE = ' NX ' ) ) ;

FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' OAKLAND ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' SALT LAKE CITY ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' NEW YORK ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' MIAMI ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' TUESDAY ' ) AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FARE . FARE_ID FROM FARE WHERE ( FARE.ONE_DIRECTION_COST < = 466 AND FARE . FARE_BASIS_CODE IN ( SELECT FARE_BASIS . FARE_BASIS_CODE FROM FARE_BASIS WHERE FARE_BASIS . BASIS_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' TUESDAY ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ;

AIRCRAFT_CODE_SEQUENCE IN ( SELECT FLIGHT . AIRCRAFT_CODE_SEQUENCE FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' CLEVELAND ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' DALLAS ' ) ) AND FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME < 1200 ) ) ) ) ) ;

CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE 1 = 1 ) ) ) ) ) ;
